These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, azalea, iris
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, september, august
1. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in september##2
6. the person who growsiris is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | iris | balloon-flower     | azalea | poppy |
| Birthday     | january     | september | august  | july      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, manager, accountant, dressmaker
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, hiking, chess, photography
1. the manager is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the accountant is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Job   | doctor | manager    | dressmaker     | accountant  |
| Hobby     | camping    | chess | hiking | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, pomegranate, cherry, pumpkin
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, superhero, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Food   | pomegranate   | cherry   | pear  | pumpkin |
| Movie-Genre           | disaster | horror | superhero | zombie  |

