.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, drama, mystery
There 4 different types of food: onion, pumpkin, kale, peach
1. the person eating peach is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person eating kale##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | family | martial-arts | mystery | drama  |
| Food   | pumpkin  | onion   | peach  | kale |

