.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, january, february
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, white, grey
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who likes grey is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Birthday   | september    | march   | january | february    |
| Color      | aquamarine | purple | white       | grey |

