.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bongani, chaman, swisher
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, fish, goldfish
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the goldfish and the chaman-smoker##2
3. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the fish and the havana-smoker##2
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Cigar    | havana | chaman | swisher | bongani |
| Pet   | snake | rat  | fish    | goldfish  |

