.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, ritmeester, oliveros, montecristo
City: miami, hamburg, liverpool, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2
5. the person traveling to hamburg is the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to liverpool and the montecristo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | cain | montecristo | oliveros | ritmeester     |
| City     | miami | boston  | hamburg   | liverpool |

