.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, turkish, french
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, november, september
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the french is the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the french is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the american is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality         | french | turkish | american | brazilian   |
| Birthday   | may | november | october      | september |

