.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, colonial, victorian
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, pilot, electrician, librarian
1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the librarian is on the far right##1
3. the librarian is the victorian house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the ranch-style house is between the pilot and the police-officer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| House     | cape-cod | ranch-style   | colonial      | victorian      |
| Job   | pilot     | electrician | police-officer | librarian |

