.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, skiing, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, december, april
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Sport   | surfing | climbing | skiing      | volleyball   |
| Birthday   | december  | february    | september | april |

