.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, aquamarine, emerald, orange
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite, sunflower, iris
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsiris is the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
5. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
6. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | green | emerald | orange    | aquamarine      |
| Flower   | sunflower       | iris       | aconite | bellflower |

