.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, bartender, coach, writer
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, backgammon, monopoly
1. the bartender is on the far right##1
2. the chef is the chef##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the bartender##3
5. the coach is on the left or right of the writer##3
6. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the writer##3
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | chef | coach  | writer | bartender |
| Game           | backgammon     | monopoly | mah-jongg    | canasta     |

