.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, country, folk, disco
4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, goldfish, lizard
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | country  | techno | disco  | folk      |
| Pet    | lizard | frog | goldfish | guinea-pig |

