4. the photographer is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the coach is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the coach is the owner of the mouse##1
7. the photographer is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Pet         | fish | hedgehog | goldfish | mouse |
| Job   | pilot     | bartender       | photographer   | coach      |

