.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, pineapple, potato, carrot
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
2. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
3. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating potato##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | pepper | carrot | potato | pineapple |
| Transport         | subway  | helicopter   | quad-bike | snowmobile     |

