.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, dunhill, vegafina, alhambra
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, bridge, canasta
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing chess##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Cigar      | oliveros | dunhill    | alhambra  | vegafina |
| Game   | chess       | scrabble | bridge | canasta  |

