.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, volleyball, handball
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, monopoly, scrabble
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Sport   | handball        | swimming       | volleyball   | basketball |
| Game    | scrabble | monopoly | domino | canasta  |

