.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
City: edinburgh, hamburg, rome, prague
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, swisher, old-henry, chaman
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the chaman-smoker is the chaman-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
4. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
6. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| City   | hamburg     | edinburgh     | rome          | prague |
| Cigar      | blend | swisher | chaman | old-henry  |

 